profile:
Expert Electric - We're your neighborhood's electrician

We provide residential and commercial electrical services to: Vancouver, North and West Vancouver, Burnaby, New Westminster, Richmond, Delta, Coquitlam area, Maple Ridge, Pitt Meadows, Surrey, Langley, White Rock, Abbotsford and Mission.

We've got the power you need! Our trained electricians are the best in the industry, and can repair any issue, guaranteed! From installations to emergencies, big or small... our electricians can perform the job. We focus on the relationship and getting you the things you need to enjoy life!

Why call us first? 

•We are easy to reach - Real people answer our phones, not machines.
•1,000’s of parts on our trucks - For on the spot repairs in your home or business.
•Well Trained Courteous Technicians - we successfully perform repair to thousands of electrical problems every year.
•Up Front Guaranteed Pricing - you know the price before the work begins.
•24 hour emergency service.
•Quick response time
•Trained electricians
•Personalized scheduling

SOME OF OUR SERVICES INCLUDE

•Ceiling Fan Installation / Maintenance
•Breakers and Fuses
•Code Corrections
•Plug Outlets and Circuits
•Track and Accent Lighting
•Service Panel Upgrades
•High-Tech Troubleshooting
•Dedicated Computer Circuits
•Telephone and Data Lines
•Lighting Design and Maintenance
•Security & Landscape Lighting
•Surge Protectors
•Motors
•Exhaust Fans
•Electric Heaters
•Transformers
•Smoke Detectors
•Ground Fault Interrupt Circuits
•Appliance Circuits
•Hot Tubs and Spas
•Standby generator installations

profile:
Electric Avenue is a licensed, Bonded, and Insured Electrical Contractor. We specialize in service work, renovations, and repairs throughout the entire lower mainland and greater Vancouver. We focus on the quality of our work, customer service, and meeting the needs of our customers. We are proud members of both the Better Business Bureau and Chamber of Commerce.

profile: Western Summit Electric Ltd. is built on a set of core values that are most important to us. We provide the highest QUALITY electrical services and settle for nothing less. We use top quality products from local wholesalers to ensure the highest level of safety and functionality for our clients. We install these products with precision and care. We will always be honest, working together with you through every step of the project – no matter how big or small. All our work is completed with a one-year warranty on labour and materials to help put your worries at ease.
